---
layout: base.njk
title: "Jason Lau - Digital Media Designer"
description: "Jason Lau is a multidisciplinary designer, mainly creating projects in the form of graphical expression."
keywords: "Jason Lau, designer, art, graphics, creative, digital art, illustrations"
h1: "Jason Lau - A Multidisciplinary Designer"
printSubtitle: "Multidisciplinary Designer"
activeRole: "Designer"
tagline: "a multidisciplinary graphic designer aiming to make technologies expressive."
introMaxWidthClass: "max-w-[580px]"
permalink: "designer.html"
---

<main id="main-content" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-4 gap-y-16 md:grid-cols-12">
  <aside class="order-2 flex flex-col md:max-w-[400px] gap-16 md:col-span-4 md:pl-24 2xl:col-span-3 2xl:-mt-[140px]">
    <section>
      {% set designerEdu = site.education | selectattr("designer") | list %}
      {% for edu in designerEdu %}
      <div class="mb-8">
        <div class="font-bold">{{ edu.degree }}</div>
        <div class="text-gray-800">{{ edu.designer.school or edu.school }}</div>
        {% if edu.designer.schoolSub %}
        <div class="text-gray-800">{{ edu.designer.schoolSub }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">{{ edu.designer.time or edu.time }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
      <div>
        {% for edu in site.education %}
        {% if edu.designerLine %}
        <div class="text-gray-800">{{ edu.designerLine }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>
  </aside>

  <div class="order-1 flex flex-col max-w-[1400px] gap-16 md:col-span-8 lg:-mt-[120px] xl:-mt-[140px] 2xl:col-span-6">
    <section class="grid w-full grid-cols-1 gap-x-12 gap-y-12 md:grid-cols-8">

      <section class="col-span-1 grid gap-x-12 gap-y-12 md:col-span-6">
        <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 h-auto w-full md:col-span-6">
          <video aria-label="Conceptual book library animation" class="h-auto w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg" autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
            <source src="design-works/book-ocean.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
          </video>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-center text-sm">
            Conceptual book library for readers to share their notes written virtually on the book pages.
          </h3>
        </article>
        <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 h-auto w-full md:col-span-6">
          <img src="design-works/google-chart.png"
               alt="Heatmap showing the distribution of latency over time."
               class="h-auto w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-center text-sm">Heatmap showing distribution over time. Used by Google Cloud.</h3>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="col-span-1 grid gap-x-12 gap-y-6 md:col-span-2">
        <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 pl-32 pr-32 md:col-span-2 md:pl-6 md:pr-6">
          <img src="design-works/rapidstream-logo.png"
               alt="A logo with a wave-like pattern for the startup RapidStream."
               class="h-auto w-full" loading="lazy">
        </article>
        <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 pl-32 pr-32 md:col-span-2 md:pl-4 md:pr-4">
          <img src="design-works/cat-logo.png"
               alt="A logo showing a cat with a cute heart."
               class="h-auto w-full" loading="lazy">
        </article>
        <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 md:col-span-2 md:pb-24 md:pl-2 md:pr-2">
          <img src="design-works/tex-user-group.jpg"
               alt="A logo with texts of 'TeX' surrounding the main text for a TeX user group event."
               class="h-auto w-full" loading="lazy">
          <h3 class="-mt-6 text-center text-sm md:mt-0">TeX user group event</h3>
        </article>
      </section>

      <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 md:col-span-3">
        <video aria-label="Impression of seasons animation" class="h-auto w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg" autoplay loop muted playsinline preload="metadata">
          <source src="design-works/seasons.mp4" type="video/mp4">
          Your browser does not support the video tag.
        </video>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-center text-sm">Impression of seasons</h3>
      </article>

      <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 md:col-span-5">
        <img src="design-works/your-image.jpg"
             alt="Photo showing a person standing in front of a screen, displaying their face in a digital art style."
             class="h-auto w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg" loading="lazy">
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-center text-sm">How you would see yourself in the AI era?</h3>
      </article>

      <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 md:col-span-4">
        <img src="design-works/self-image.png"
             alt="Photo showing how artists depict themselves in their works."
             class="h-auto w-full" loading="lazy">
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-center text-sm">
          This is how artists viewed themselves in their works. We averaged their self-portraits.
          Left: Renaissance, Right: Modern.
        </h3>
      </article>

      <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 md:col-span-4">
        <img src="design-works/uploaded-image.jpg"
             alt="Photo showing how students see themselves by comparing on-site capture and self-uploaded images."
             class="h-auto w-full" loading="lazy">
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-center text-sm">
          This is how young adults viewed themselves in their portraits. We averaged their photos.
          Left: On-site capture, Right: Self-uploaded.
        </h3>
      </article>

      <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 md:col-span-6">
        <img src="design-works/tuna-icons.png"
             alt="Icons designed for TUNA association, featuring the icon for the mirror site, DNS service, NTP service, and the danmaku service."
             class="h-auto w-full" loading="lazy">
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-center text-sm">Icons designed for Tsinghua University TUNA association.</h3>
      </article>

      <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 pl-32 pr-32 md:col-span-2 md:pl-0 md:pr-0">
        <img src="design-works/pika-logo.png"
             alt="A polyline drawing of a pikachu holding the number 42."
             class="h-auto w-full" loading="lazy">
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-center text-sm">Logo 42</h3>
      </article>

      <article class="col-span-1 mb-6 grid grid-cols-1 items-end gap-x-12 md:col-span-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="col-span-1">
          <img src="design-works/thermal-printer.jpg"
               alt="An experiment with thermal printer, printing a photo in black and white."
               class="h-auto w-full" loading="lazy">
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-1 text-center text-sm md:text-left">
          An experiment with thermal printer before the popularization of Paperang (喵喵机). It prints out a photo on the go with a QR code attached for the original image, allowing sharing of the photo with someone met on the street.
        </div>
      </article>

    </section>
  </div>
</main>
